76561198009127998,Recommended,589760,32008539,Posted: 27 May,all,Warmonger,"Fantastic ultra fun game!!! Different than any other game you will find. You buy cars and fix them to go driving around a free roam open world map and go racing.Building and Repairing-	The vehicle building and repairing portion of the game is the best out of any other game I have ever played. Adding and removing parts to and from cars is quick and easy, one mouse click per part.-	You can buy cars and trucks ranging from brand new to totaled off wrecks and everything in between. At the beginning you won’t have much money so the cars you will be able to buy will need allot of work. Once you have bought your first vehicle you can either buy parts you need or buy and part out wrecks until you have what you need to build something that runs.-	Most of the parts can be swapped between vehicles. You can make cars into off road racers or trucks into drag cars. There is an extraordinarily wide variety of options for doing what you want to the vehicles.Driving-	Weather you spend the time to do a total frame off restoration or fix a vehicle up so it barely runs you can leave your garage and go free roaming around a fairly decent size map. This is what makes this game different than anything else I have played. You can drive around the map at your leisure, find people to drag race with, drive to a race track and race, go and fill up with gas or just drive around and see what there is to see. I don’t know of any other car building games that let you just go out and drive around and do whatever you want to.-	Racing includes street racing with AI characters you find on the map as well as on four designated race tracks. One oval dirt track, one off road course, one oval paved race track and one paved race course.Note:There have been some unfavorable reviews due to the handling of the cars in this game but with the update on May 26th those issues have been fixed and the cars now handle beautifully!I would highly recommend this game to anyone and everyone!!!"
