76561198124930291,Recommended,589760,34073688,Posted: 6 August,all,Badger,"I love this game! Buuuuuut, It's not without it's problems.So here's a neat little pro and con list for ya!--PROS--LOTS of customisation. There's not a whole lot that can't be interchanged between the 7 cars in the game.Degrading car performance. Might seem like a small thing but not many games actually do this. The more you race your car, the more damaged the internal parts get and the performance degrades, then failures are a strong possibility.Fuel. You need it. It's not a game to refill it for you either after a race or a drive. Just like real life, YOU need to fill it up when it's low.Fluids. Like Fuel, Fluid levels drop and in the case of Oil, needs to be changed when it gets old.The Fluids that are in the game are: Oil, Coolant and something I've never seen before simulated in a game, Battery water level.Many many races and things to do.Make a ' Mad Max ' car. Seriously, you can do this! You can quite literally create a frankenstein car thats made up of parts of many cars.Gauges: Speedo, Tacho, Fuel, Oil temp, Water temp ( overheating is a thing ), Battery charge level, Alternator output. All with mulitple different looks so you can make essentially a custom dash layout.Game itself runs pretty nicely, I've had no crashes and no bugs that I've seen. Also runs at a constant 60 FPS.--CONS--Horrendus driving controls: Seriously they are terrible. Don't even bother with a Keyboard, It's undrivable. I used an Xbox controller and it works much better but still pretty bad. A good thing to note is you do get used to it after a while.Physics: Kinda same with the controls, Pretty bad. Though once again you do get used to it.Graphics: Cars look pretty good but the world graphics are pretty bad.Mod Support: None yet and it's kinda a shame. This game would lend itself well to Mods.Repeating secondhand cars and parts: This is a small niggle of mine, Theres a ' newspaper ' ingame which you buy cars and parts from. The niggle is that after a while you see the same cars in the same configuration time after time. I love to be able to put in more variations.-------------------This game is different in a lot of ways and I love it for that!If they improved the physics and the controls plus added Mod support or just added a little more variety in this game, It'd be perfect.That being said, for me, the pros far outweigh the cons and I most certainly recommend you to try this little gem!"
